Invocation Name: thoughts of dog
des:
Thoughts of Dog gives you a look into the beautiful mind of the best doggo on Twitter, @dog_feelings. Keep up with the latest news on fren, the skittle under the fridge, the human, Sebastian, the horrors of sky booms and the wonders of snoozles. @dog_feelings is an account created by Matt Nelson, developer of www.weratedogs.com. Rover.com says, "If a dog could tweet, this is pretty much exactly what they’d have to say."

You can say:

"Alexa, open Thoughts of Dog"
"Alexa, start Thoughts of Dog"
"Alexa, launch Thoughts of Dog"

Please leave a 5-star review if you love this skill, because who doesn't love a good doggo
